{"tid":900304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台已死！連迪洛夫當選2018年瑞典足球先生都冇人講！","createTime":"2018-11-13T06:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T06:06:26.000Z","uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0c405ca4c269eba94a07e912a0209df827c9296e","tid":900304,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"香港時間11月13日，曼聯中堅連迪路夫當選為2018年瑞典足球先生。<br />\n<br />\n　　連迪路夫現年24歲，今季代表曼聯出場14次，今年他代表瑞典出戰俄羅斯世界盃，是球隊主力球員之一。伊巴謙莫域曾在2007-2016年連續10年當選瑞典足球先生，2017年格蘭基斯特打破了他的壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTqhWTZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTqhWTZ.png&h=0c06d8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BATrQd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBATrQd0.png&h=a3482356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b095f2b682a0f9573b0358ec740234c28cc62d0","tid":900304,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"@N_Ben"},{"pid":"efd013ddfa6666074a816e3d668a77c3dad9548f","tid":900304,"uid":154872,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"辣殺都要理?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1fe57007b7e820c8e50a4c58101974d48f3d57","tid":900304,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"efd013ddfa6666074a816e3d668a77c3dad9548f","tid":900304,"uid":154872,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"辣殺都要理?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba7cabde072ba63f7a63688fce8a6195d7c2adc","t